reviewText: Big disappointment. Expected much more detailed footage of Neuschwanstein.

I've been to these castles, and this video does all of them great justice.  The color is superb, and the narration is excellent.  I actually ordered this video for someone else, who let me view it when I delivered it to him.  When I got home, I ordered my own copy.  It is now one of my favorite DVD's.
